title: Week 4 Liquidity Mining Proposal
body:
This marks the fourth week of liquidity mining on Balancer v2. The Ballers propose allocating 2500 BAL to each of the following pools for the week starting Monday, June 14th at 00:00 UTC:

USDC/WETH 50/50 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0x96646936b91d6b9d7d0c47c496afbf3d6ec7b6f8000200000000000000000019
SNX/WETH 50/50 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0x072f14b85add63488ddad88f855fda4a99d6ac9b000200000000000000000027
LINK/WETH 50/50 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0xe99481dc77691d8e2456e5f3f61c1810adfc1503000200000000000000000018
COMP/WETH 50/50 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0xefaa1604e82e1b3af8430b90192c1b9e8197e377000200000000000000000021
REN/WETH 50/50 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0xec60a5fef79a92c741cb74fdd6bfc340c0279b01000200000000000000000015

The Ballers propose upgrading the following pool, allocating 5000 additional BAL for the week starting Monday, June 14th at 00:00 UTC:

BAL/WETH 80/20 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0x5c6ee304399dbdb9c8ef030ab642b10820db8f56000200000000000000000014

The pull request reflecting these changes can be found here: https://github.com/balancer-labs/frontend-v2/pull/421
